# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore for the Dataverse MCP File Manager (.NET 10 solution)
#   - class library + console demo + Windows cfapi Explorer host
#   - sparse-package build (PowerShell) under src/DataverseFileManager.Explorer/Package/
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- .NET build output ---
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
TestResults/
[Tt]est[Rr]esults/

# CsWin32 generated sources emitted for inspection (CompilerGeneratedFilesOutputPath)
**/obj/generated/

# --- Sparse-package build outputs (src/DataverseFileManager.Explorer/Package/) ---
# Keep AppxManifest.xml + setup-sparse-package.ps1 (the source); ignore everything built.
**/Package/stage/
*.msix
*.msixbundle
*.appx
*.appxbundle
*.appxsym
*.appxupload

# --- Local connection config (real per-deployment values) ---
# Keep appsettings.example.json (the template); ignore the filled-in copy.
appsettings.json
**/appsettings.json

# --- Signing material (never commit certs/keys) ---
*.pfx
*.cer
*.snk

# --- Visual Studio / Rider / editor noise ---
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.DotSettings.user

# --- NuGet ---
*.nupkg
packages/
.nuget/

# --- OS / misc ---
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.log
